'''金馬創投會議'''（{{lang-en|Taipei Golden Horse Film Project Promotion}}，[[簡稱|簡稱]]：FPP）是創立於2007年提供[[華語電影|華語電影]]相關創作者與電影發行商之間所設的投資平台<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201506040008-1.aspx |title = 金馬創投分享會 大馬歡喜交流 |author = 郭朝河 |date = 2015-01-08 |publisher = 中央社 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-09-24 |archive-date = 2015-09-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925125145/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201506040008-1.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=163549 |title = 台法電影創投工作坊啟動 5國片企劃入選 |author = 江昭倫 |date = 2015-01-08 |publisher = 中央廣播電臺 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-09-24 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150628083946/http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=163549 |archivedate = 2015年6月28日 |df =  }}</ref>。

== 歷史沿革 ==
2014年新增2項「臺北文創劇作獎」及「華聯國際最具潛力創意獎」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20141117000105-260204 |title = 逾10國投資人跨海登台 搶華語電影企畫案 |author = 邱莉玲 |date = 2014-11-17 |publisher = 中國時報 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-09-24 |archive-date = 2015-09-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925121000/http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20141117000105-260204 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。該年度是[[華聯國際|華聯國際多媒體股份有限公司]]成為首度參與金馬創投會議、並於會議中設立獎項的公司<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1158908 |title = 華聯國際攜手金馬創投 30萬獎金鼓勵優秀華人作品 |author = 徐卉 |date = 2014-11-16 |publisher = 自由時報 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2015-09-24 |archive-date = 2015-09-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925125919/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1158908 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。並在2015年首次將入選上限名額增加至30組<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://udn.com/news/story/8706/1301553 |title = 金馬創投現金獎加碼 侯孝賢率兩高徒對談 |author = 項貽斐 |date = 2015-11-08 |publisher = 聯合報 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2016-04-05 |archive-date = 2016-04-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160415062637/http://udn.com/news/story/8706/1301553 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2020年4月29日官方宣布增設劇集企劃項目，提供華語劇集企劃能與國際影視投資者媒合平臺<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/entertain/202004/202004291998787.html |title = 2020金馬獎增設「劇集」企劃 各項報名6/1起展開 |author = 洪立文 |date = 2020-04-29 |publisher = 華視新聞 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2020-04-29 |archive-date = 2020-05-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200505020739/https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/entertain/202004/202004291998787.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

